        "title": "Two powerful earthquakes hit Venezuela",
        "title_zh": "委内瑞拉接连遭遇两次强震",
        "url": "https://www.economist.com/node/2026-06-27/22",
        "summary_md": "### 🌟 一句话核心主旨\n2026年6月24日委内瑞拉在极短时间内接连发生两次强震(7.2级与7.5级),震中均位于首都加拉加斯以西,造成重大人员伤亡,美国地质调查局警告死亡人数可能高达万人。\n\n### 🔍 核心观点与论据拆解\n- **双震罕见性**:两场地震在24小时内紧密接连发生,第二次震中距第一次仅16公里,地震学上称为「双震」(doublet),此类现象极为罕见。\n- **具体震级与位置**:美国地质调查局(USGS)测定第一次地震震级为7.2级,震中位于加拉加斯以西170公里处;第二次为7.5级,发生于震中16公里外。\n- **官方伤亡通报**:委内瑞拉代理总统德尔西·罗德里格斯(DELCY RODRíGUEZ)通报称,目前已有32人死亡、700人受伤,但承认死亡人数将继续上升。\n- **USGS死亡预测**:美国地质调查局估计,死亡人数达到10,000人的概率高达44%,暗示灾情可能远比官方当前数字严重。\n- **时点信息**:文章发布于2026年6月25日,灾害发生于6月24日,信息发布与救援仍在进行中。\n\n### 🤨 争议与潜在挑战\n原文未涉及明显争议。\n\n### 🔮 未来趋势预判\n鉴于「双震」属罕见地质事件且伴随高震级,后续余震风险不容忽视;USGS高达44%的万人死亡概率预测表明,实际伤亡数字大概率将继续攀升,委内瑞拉执政当局的救援与统计能力将面临严峻考验。",
        "content_raw": "<p><span class=\"te_section_title\">The Americas</span><span class=\"te_fly_span\"> | Devastation in Caracas</span></p>\n<h1>Two powerful earthquakes hit Venezuela</h1>\n<h3>Such tightly sequenced quakes are rare</h3>\n<h3>June 25th 2026</h3>\n<p>Two powerful earthquakes hit Venezuela in quick succession on June 24th. The United States Geological Survey (USGS) said the first had a magnitude of 7.2, with an epicentre 170km west of Caracas, the capital. The second measured 7.5 and hit 16km away. Such tightly sequenced “doublet” quakes are rare. Delcy Rodríguez, Venezuela’s acting president, said 32 people had been killed and 700 injured, but the death toll will climb. USGS reckons there’s a 44% chance that 10,000 are dead. <span class=\"span_ufinish\">■</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.economist.com/newsletters/el-boletin\">Sign up to El Boletín</a>, our subscriber-only newsletter on Latin America, to understand the forces shaping a fascinating and complex region.</p>\n<p>This article was downloaded by <a class=\"producer_link\" href=\"https://z-lib.io\">zlibrary</a> from <a class=\"origin_link\" href=\"https://www.economist.com//the-americas/2026/06/25/two-powerful-earthquakes-hit-venezuela\">https://www.economist.com//the-americas/2026/06/25/two-powerful-earthquakes-hit-venezuela</a> </p>"
