        "content_raw": "<p><span class=\"te_section_title\">Economic &amp; financial indicators</span><span class=\"te_fly_span\"> | Indicators</span></p>\n<h1>Economic data, commodities and markets</h1>\n<h3>June 25th 2026</h3>\n<p>This article was downloaded by <a class=\"producer_link\" href=\"https://z-lib.io\">zlibrary</a> from <a class=\"origin_link\" href=\"https://www.economist.com//economic-and-financial-indicators/2026/06/25/economic-data-commodities-and-markets\">https://www.economist.com//economic-and-financial-indicators/2026/06/25/economic-data-commodities-and-markets</a> </p>",
